## **Success Metrics: What Good Looks Like**

**User successfully uses the tool when they:**

1. ✅ Build 2-3 distinct scenarios to compare  
2. ✅ Discover a pressure point they hadn't considered (e.g., "I didn't realize retention was eating 40% of growth")  
3. ✅ Make a strategic choice based on trade-offs (e.g., "I'll pursue Scenario B because I can't hire that fast")  
4. ✅ Return monthly to update scenarios as business evolves

**User is confused when they:**

1. ❌ Don't understand what sliders do or how they interact  
2. ❌ Can't tell which scenario is "better" (charts don't clarify)  
3. ❌ Feel overwhelmed by too many metrics at once  
4. ❌ Don't know what to do with the insights (no clear next action)

